code: @Override public IndexUpgradeInfoRequest indices(String... indices) {     this.indices = Objects.requireNonNull(indices, "indices cannot be null").     return this. }
public void indicesOptions(IndicesOptions indicesOptions) {     this.indicesOptions = indicesOptions. }

@Override public boolean equals(Object o) {     if (this == o)         return true.     if (o == null || getClass() != o.getClass())         return false.     IndexUpgradeInfoRequest request = (IndexUpgradeInfoRequest) o.     return Arrays.equals(indices, request.indices) && Objects.equals(indicesOptions.toString(), request.indicesOptions.toString()). }
@Override public int hashCode() {     return Objects.hash(Arrays.hashCode(indices), indicesOptions.toString()). }
